{
  "stem": "24470.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--incidents that, uh, they were screaming at prisoners.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were shouting.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were, uh, hitting, you know, in the face.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there was one row of machines that had a wires brush turning very, very fast.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And, uh, the-- the shells were put-- the anti-aircraft shells were put into the brush by the prisoners to clean them inside, to polish them.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I remember one woman prisoner, who was obviously tired, fell asleep or bent her head.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And her whole hair, scalp was torn by the machine.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So we worked there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I'll come now to the, uh, story of my little heart and chain, which I'll show you later.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I wore-- my watch and my ring were taken by the Germans off at the time where they took us out from home.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They just checked everything and tore everything they saw.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Give me the watch.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Give me the ring.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And, fast, fast, fast.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So of course, we gave everything.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Under all the layer of clothes, which they didn't have time to look for, obviously, I had a heart, that was given-- a golden heart that was given to me by my parents on my last birthday on a golden chain.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "When I came to camp, I wore a skirt.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And somehow I-- I made a little, uh, tiny entering hole in that, uh, waistline-- waistband and put the heart and the chain in it to keep it.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "It was my only thing from home.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "We have no pictures, nothing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Um, and during the work-- labor camp, on, uh-- on my machine where I worked, there were three people working.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "One of them was a Polish woman.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Muszka, her name was.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And she used to come to that-- Muszka, M-U-S-Z-K-A.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "She used to come to camp daily.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
